<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٢ - <span class="c2">(١٥٣٩)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَاهُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7021">يَحْيَى بْنُ يَحْيَى </a>،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6709">هُشَيْمٌ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6932">يَحْيَى بْنِ سَعِيدٍ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ،<span class="c5"> غَيْرَ أَنَّهُ قَالَ:</span> وَالْعَرِيَّةُ: النَّخْلَةُ، تُجْعَلُ لِلْقَوْمِ فَيَبِيعُونَهَا بِخَرْصِهَا تَمْرًا .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>